### =====================================================
### 9. Veteran books all slots (7 appointments across the week)
### =====================================================

### 9a. Book Monday morning
POST {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots/{{slotMon1}}/book
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "urgent": false
}

### 9b. Book Monday afternoon
POST {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots/{{slotMon2}}/book
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "urgent": false
}

### 9c. Book Tuesday
